graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller Manager<br/>Manages DSPA Lifecycle]
    end

    subgraph "DSPA Instance (per namespace)"
        APIServer[DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, 8887/TCP gRPC<br/>KFP v2 API]
        PersistAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Watches Workflows, Persists Metadata]
        ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>Manages Recurring Runs]
        ArgoController[Argo Workflow Controller<br/>Executes Pipeline Tasks]

        subgraph "Optional Components"
            MLMD[ML Metadata gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>Artifact Lineage]
            MLMDEnvoy[ML Metadata Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>mTLS Support]
            MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>Metadata Storage]
            Minio[Minio<br/>9000/TCP HTTP<br/>S3-compatible Storage]
        end

        APIServer -->|persists to| MariaDB
        PersistAgent -->|writes to| MariaDB
        PersistAgent -->|watches| ArgoController
        ScheduledWF -->|creates workflows| ArgoController
        APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies to| MLMD
        MLMD -->|stores in| MariaDB
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
        PipelineCR[Pipeline CR v2beta1]
        ScheduledWorkflowCR[ScheduledWorkflow CR]
        WorkflowCR[Workflow CR<br/>Argo]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        ExternalS3[External S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS/Compatible]
        ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL]
    end

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Pipeline Management UI]
        Workbench[Workbenches/Notebooks<br/>KFP SDK Client]
        Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>Prometheus]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWF
    Controller -->|deploys| ArgoController
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| MariaDB
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| Minio
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| MLMD

    User -->|creates| PipelineCR
    User -->|creates| ScheduledWorkflowCR
    PipelineCR -->|processed by| APIServer
    ScheduledWorkflowCR -->|processed by| ScheduledWF
    ArgoController -->|creates| WorkflowCR

    APIServer -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    ArgoController -->|manages pods| K8sAPI
    APIServer -->|optional external| ExternalS3
    APIServer -->|optional external| ExternalDB

    Dashboard -->|API calls| APIServer
    Workbench -->|KFP SDK| APIServer
    Monitoring -->|scrapes /metrics| Controller
    Monitoring -->|scrapes /metrics| APIServer

    ArgoController -->|executes tasks in| WorkflowPods[Workflow Task Pods<br/>Ephemeral]
    WorkflowPods -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    WorkflowPods -->|stores artifacts| ExternalS3
    WorkflowPods -->|reports metadata| MLMD

